{
  "target": "MaximumLikelihood",
  "kind": "model_estimation",
  "source": "SMOKE (M13): self-computed values from this port's own C++ build (core/build), NOT C#-oracle values -- M14 re-pins them against the real RMC.BestFit. Exercises the `competing_risks` model type: component families through the factory into CompetingRisksModel -- which is NOT an IUnivariateModel (the C# omits it) but IS a ModelBase, which is all the estimators require. Parameter layout: the concatenated component parameters [Gumbel location, Gumbel scale, Weibull scale, Weibull shape]. LOOSE smoke tolerances (rel 1e-6).",
  "datasets": {
    "annual_peaks": [
      12500,
      15300,
      9870,
      21000,
      18400,
      11200,
      26800,
      14100,
      19500,
      11600
    ]
  },
  "cases": [
